message_text: Emphasized Apologies for the late text. Just wrapped staging the remaining sites in the AWS VPS. Took us the entire time since before we began texting at 8p, just so you have an understanding of how long this process takes. There are still a few stragglers we are working through (namely backups with large file sizes), but Christian believes he found a solution for how to deal with them. Will keep you posted. In the meantime, we will be ready probably around tomorrow afternoon to begin having you cut over nameservers. I need to do one more sweep of the DNS records for each domain to make sure we have all of the records in place before we cut over. Have a good night.

Liked Clarification. We still need to unzip several of the files, but they have been migrated from our OneDrive onto each sites respective installation. So once we unzip and log in with the proper credentials, we can smoke test and then have you point NS at Cloudflare which will complete the cutover.
Can we prioritize Window Film Solutions out of all of those today? Theyre wanting to make edits to their own site soon
Whatever you need man  ready to do it now?
Also got a late text from AE. Apparently that form with the year/make/model dropdown isnt emailing them. Do we setup SMTP for their site? That form should be going to orders@automotiveelegancellc.com
